content.rendered:
We have received a nice order from far away, exotic Vietnam. We are going to build a Alumax Worker 41 Firefighter that will patrol part of the Vietnamese coast. The more than twelve meters long an 4.5 meters wide aluminum Worker will be equipped with, among other things, a highly advanced fire extinguishing system, 2x 480HP Mercury Marine diesel engines and HamiltonJet. The delivery date is spring 2021.

[Photo: The Alumax Worker 33 of the Scheveningen Port Authority is smaller than the Worker 41 but otherwise quite similar]
